snippet.title: FINAL FANTASY VII REBIRTH – First Look Trailer
snippet.description:
Here’s a first look at FINAL FANTASY VII REBIRTH, the sequel to 2020’s critically-acclaimed FINAL FANTASY VII REMAKE.

This next standalone chapter in the FINAL FANTASY VII remake trilogy will launch next Winter.

Make sure you’re following us for all the latest FINAL FANTASY VII news:
